  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChoicePair
    This class manages a mapping of a label and a flag, where the label represents an ID of an image file and the flag represents whether or not the candidate(s) to which the image file corresponds was selected by the voter.
    HTMLPrinter
    A class which provides tools to write images to HTML files.
    Printer
    This class handles all print calls made by Voteboxes, Supervisors and any future additions that will need to print
    PrintImageUtils
    A class which provides image manipulation support for printing
    QRCodeGenerator
    Slightly modified version of code found at http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2489048/qr-code-encoding-and-decoding-using-zxing utilizing the ZXing QR code library
    RaceTitlePair
    This class manages a mapping of a label and an image.
